OL,5, It's a moment dreaded by head teachers 
OL,6, - when the phone rings to tell you     
OL,7, government inspectors are on the way to
OL,8, assess your school. For Ruth Perry that
OL,9, call came in November 2022. While      
OL,10, waiting for Ofsted to publish their    
OL,11, report and fearing losing her job, Mrs 
OL,12, Perry killed herself.                  
OL,14,FHere other head teachers talk frankly  
OL,15,Fabout the mental health impact Ofsted  
OL,16,Finspections have had on them. Some of  
OL,17,Ftheir accounts are upsetting.          
